Moodle Plugin for Camtasia Relay Notification plugin

Installation:
Download the source files
Copy source files to a folder name "camtasia_relay"
Copy the "camtasia_relay" folder to moodle/local folder on the Moodle Server
Login as the admin to the Moodle server
Allow the plugin to install
Setup a Web Service role with permisions to use "Xml-RPC" and to "Start discussions"
Add a user as a Web Service role
Create a token under Plugins > Web Services > Manage Tokens for the user and the Camtasia Relay plugin
On Relay enter the token generated in the Notification Server page